                        carel_description "A process shall be employed for verifying that a product or a patch is not released until its security related issues have been addressed and tracked to closure (see 10.5, DM-4: Addressing security related issues). This includes issues associated with: e) defect management (see Clause 10, Practice 6 – Management of security-related issues)."
